'''Bone Fragments''' are special [[:Category:Resources|resources]] that can be dropped by [[Skeleton]]s and [[Lava Lurk]]s when slain, by destroying [[Mining#Mining Nodes|Bone Nodes]] on [[Ginger Island]], by destroying crates and barrels in [[Skull Cavern]], and in [[Artifact Spot]]s.

==Bone Mill==
Five Bone Fragments can be turned into [[Quality Fertilizer]], [[Speed-Gro]], [[Deluxe Speed-Gro]] or [[Tree Fertilizer]] in the [[Bone Mill]].

==Trade==
The [[Island Trader]] on [[Ginger Island]] trades, as permanent stock:
*1 [[Taro Tuber]] for 2 bone fragments
*The [[Banana Pudding]] recipe for 30 bone fragments

